{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, risk awareness of LLMs is a significant factor for the safe execution of LLM agents.",
    "Here, we formulate the task of agent safety monitor to evaluate the risk awareness of LLMs.",
    "Task Formulation of Agent Safety Monitor.",
    "As illustrated in Figure 2, an LLM checks agent interaction records to judge if the agent actions are safe.",
    "The performance as a safety monitor demonstrates whether the LLM can effectively identify the safety risks and make correct judgments, revealing its risk awareness."
  ]
}